{"tid":2185033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易】美國延長部份中國關稅豁免　直至年底","createTime":"2020-09-02T04:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:40:44.000Z","uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cc278cd88330d6e0dc9a1b1c63623e343e5c0584","tid":2185033,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:07:26.000Z","msg":"美國貿易代表辦公室9月1日宣布延長部份中國商品關稅豁免，包括智能手錶和特定醫療口罩，不過豁免期限只延長至年底，而不是如過往一樣延長一根據《聯邦政府紀事》告示，延長適用於一年前根據「301條款」徵收7.5%關稅的3,000億美元中國商品以外的產品，包括藍芽和可穿戴數據傳輸設備，例如蘋果公司（Apple）、FitBit、Sonos和其他科技公司從中國進口的產品"},{"pid":"7f217346810adef1daee95b5d228523c2a8ca93f","tid":2185033,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T09:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657fd3f51a922951c401951d0c6977a0c3755bfa","tid":2185033,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c075b926f1c9015c54e7de36e32f30e3df0dbe","tid":2185033,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433d89fe095ce10ee9d6a40a14d206b7810cf192","tid":2185033,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"應該係想用哂啲晶片存貨先？"}]}